# ricDAE Test Plan (Skeleton)

## Scope
Tests ensure ingestion pipelines, normalization, and MCP tool adapters operate reliably and respect governance guardrails.

## Planned Suites
- `test_ingestion_jobs.py`: Validate connector fetch logic against fixtures and timeout handling
- `test_normalization.py`: Verify metadata schemas and deduplication rules
- `test_mcp_tools.py`: Exercise MCP endpoints (`research_update`, `literature_search`, `trend_digest`)
- `test_governance.py`: Confirm kill-switch + ToS compliance behaviours

## WSP Alignment
- WSP 5: Coverage target ≥90%
- WSP 6: Auditable test execution with command examples
- WSP 34: Documentation produced alongside implementation

> Status: Pending implementation once Phase 1 ingestion code lands.
